{"tid":1763854,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】行動嘅Q&A已出【行動po求推】","createTime":"2019-11-30T16:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T04:41:16.000Z","uid":311583,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f88c1c31767b16bda2e8be8fe74e4eecb4d4c7c0","tid":1763854,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:04:01.000Z","msg":"以下係今次稅局行動嘅Q&amp;A<br />\n<br />\n<strong>個行動有咩目的？</strong><br />\n今次行動目的，最主要就係癱瘓稅局。晨曦黎明，我哋吹咗兩個禮拜雞，始終叫唔郁罷工；發動全港堵路，又因為範圍太大而無法持續。既然如此，點解單獨針對一個政府機構癱瘓佢，又能集中手足人力，又能單日見果效呢？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>堵塞稅局嘅運作機制？</strong><br />\n稅局接放工，旨在令員工工作時數減少，降低人工作效率。試諗吓人地一日可以完成嘅工作，中途突然收工，就變咗兩日先完成到。<br />\nP.S. 與交一蚊稅Bot配套使用效果更佳。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>點解係稅局？</strong><br />\n明明白白話畀傳媒同國際聽，我哋唔想交稅畀個咁差嘅政府，拒絕警隊用港人交嘅稅款嚟射香港人。稅款來自市民，而民心所向，就係將稅款用喺成立獨立調查委員會，或者重組警隊上，而非用嚟助長警方濫暴。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>會唔會分薄勇武？</strong><br />\n去稅局係相對低門檻嘅和平行動，唔係個個都有條件衝前線。稍為和理非啲嘅嚟稅局，勇武自己小隊做嘢，不必預約，冇分薄可言。<br />\n和理非同勇武從來都要雙管齊下，why not both？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>會唔會失民心？</strong><br />\n其實同塞鐵一樣，手足如果人少，就要被逼做出樣衰動作，例如阻礙𨋢門關閉，以致失民心。今次行動務求人多自然塞，唔做樣衰動作，成功就保民心，失敗就失民心。<br />\n<br />\n另外，舊事重提一下：稅局行動始於6月21成功接放工。8月26、9月16稅局都有行動，前後民意冇反撲之餘，行動進行期間仲有唔少稅局公務員停低圍觀，更甚者有一齊叫口號。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>會唔會係送頭搏拉？</strong><br />\n愈近寫字樓、愈多街外人，被拉嘅幾率愈低，相信半年來大家深有體會。商場唱歌畀狗咬，因為商場唔係辦公室；和理非維園集會被驅散，因為嗰度除咗手足冇其他人。唔似機場入得唔出得，稅局隔離有入境事務大樓、政府大樓之類建築，單係疏散公務員都已經需要一定時間，要驅散嘅門檻高。即使手足要走，都有足夠嘅緩衝時間。<br />\n<br />\n當見到或收到風，公務員提早放工，離開稅務大樓，Admin就會密切注意各哨Channel，合理安排參加行動嘅手足離開。Admin亦有準備逃生路線同行動攻略，將會喺Channel發佈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=7e9ab7db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=4b259f14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"f249e4a03b4bb6039e2aa54779f486456adcab55","tid":1763854,"uid":199227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33a755ecd20c201327c03954905d3661643db87","tid":1763854,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:58:31.000Z","msg":"pp"},{"pid":"b1be8abfdea48d6ef6e760e1628e18808c13048b","tid":1763854,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T18:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc07912e4db458e1a087d57fc83e27a62a599bf1","tid":1763854,"uid":49614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T18:18:52.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"f08284ec942741c5f3812d7ad3cffc50d687b177","tid":1763854,"uid":213703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T18:59:04.000Z","msg":"行動喇休息夠喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd484ea279b667f1b91af524a174b5035e64c4f","tid":1763854,"uid":146834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T19:10:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35b22be90c6d2e379d5f545128aba861018d121c","tid":1763854,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T19:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EKpGAZvVUAEvTCJ?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEKpGAZvVUAEvTCJ%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=aedab068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n12月1日有遊行，切記切記切記 唔好再打陣地戰呀<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eBNkHS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eBNkHS</a>"},{"pid":"8c418d94036602067cd4bb8fb3f8b325fdba9ca7","tid":1763854,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff49ed2814a3f342f1b564d620d2f5a0a32c28cc","tid":1763854,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T03:44:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"adcbae9901ba39052beba4e4468a16f2bbeb1cc4","tid":1763854,"uid":321048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:41:16.000Z","msg":"做野啦"}]}